@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "FeedbackManagementPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "FeedbackManagementController" as Controller
participant "FeedbackManagementService" as Service
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Admin, DB: INCIDENT DIRECTION (ADMIN)

Admin -> View : 1. Open incident management screen
View -> Controller : 2. loadPendingIncidents()
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 3. getIncidentsByStatus('CHO_XU_LY')
activate Service
Service -> DB : 4. SELECT * FROM PHAN_HOI WHERE trang_thai = 'CHO_XU_LY'
activate DB
DB -->> Service : 5. incidentList
Deactivate DB
Service -->> Controller : 6. incidentList
Deactivate Service
Controller -->> View : 7. Render incident list
Deactivate Controller

Admin -> View : 8. Assign staff and update status
View -> Controller : 9. updateIncidentStatus(incidentId, 'DANG_SUA')
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 10. updateIncidentStatus(incidentId, status)
activate Service
Service -> DB : 11. UPDATE PHAN_HOI SET trang_thai = ? WHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB -->> Service : 12. Success
Deactivate DB
Service -->> Controller : 13. Update success
Deactivate Service
Controller -->> View : 14. Refresh list and show message
Deactivate Controller
@enduml
